---
---

<section class="bg-beige py-20 md:py-28">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
    <div class="text-center mb-14">
      <p class="animate-on-scroll text-orange font-bold text-sm tracking-widest mb-4" data-animation="fade-in">EXPERTISE</p>
      <h2 class="animate-on-scroll text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black text-navy leading-tight" data-animation="fade-up">
        多岐にわたる指導領域
      </h2>
    </div>

    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <!-- 4 Quadrants -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 sm:gap-6">
        <div class="animate-on-scroll bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 sm:p-8 text-center hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow" data-animation="fade-up" data-delay="0.1s">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 mx-auto mb-4 bg-navy/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-navy" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M13 7h8m0 0v8m0-8l-8 8-4-4-6 6"></path></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-navy text-base sm:text-lg mb-2">営業・マーケティング</h3>
          <p class="text-xs sm:text-sm text-navy">売上アップ、営業ムダとりメソッド</p>
        </div>

        <div class="animate-on-scroll bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 sm:p-8 text-center hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow" data-animation="fade-up" data-delay="0.2s">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 mx-auto mb-4 bg-orange/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-orange" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M9.75 17L9 20l-1 1h8l-1-1-.75-3M3 13h18M5 17h14a2 2 0 002-2V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z"></path></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-navy text-base sm:text-lg mb-2">DX推進</h3>
          <p class="text-xs sm:text-sm text-navy">アナログ業務のデジタル化支援</p>
        </div>

        <div class="animate-on-scroll bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 sm:p-8 text-center hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow" data-animation="fade-up" data-delay="0.3s">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 mx-auto mb-4 bg-navy/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-navy" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z"></path></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-navy text-base sm:text-lg mb-2">組織・人事</h3>
          <p class="text-xs sm:text-sm text-navy">リーダー養成、人事評価制度の構築</p>
        </div>

        <div class="animate-on-scroll bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 sm:p-8 text-center hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow" data-animation="fade-up" data-delay="0.4s">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 mx-auto mb-4 bg-orange/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-orange" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z"></path></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-navy text-base sm:text-lg mb-2">経営戦略</h3>
          <p class="text-xs sm:text-sm text-navy">中期経営計画の策定・実行支援</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p class="animate-on-scroll text-center text-sm text-navy mt-10 max-w-lg mx-auto" data-animation="fade-in" data-delay="0.5s">
        クライアントの状況に合わせ、これらの知見を総動員してアドバイスを行います。
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
